    :shortdes: Claude recommends the acoustic ownership test
    :tags: AI | Humor | Tech

.The acoustic ownership test to figure out if some part of your system is still needed: turn it off and see if anybody yells at you.

.Claude suggested this today to figure out why I put a problematic line in some
configuration file, and I can't even blame it because that's probably what I
would have done anyway:

